<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Title</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/StartPage.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/ModalSignUp.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/deal-page.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="start-page-wrapper">
    <section class="text-sections">
        <div class="logo">
        <p>MyNewHabits</p>
        <button class='button-task' id='showLogIn'>Log in</button>
        <button class='button-task' id='showSignUp'>Sign up</button>
        </div>
        <div class="quote">
        <p>your chance to make new habits</p>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
        <p>With this application tou will have a chance to improve you life.
            Our habits - our health, our life, our happiness.
            You will be able to track doing your deals.
            It is much more better to take all your daily deals than store them in your head.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="picture-section">
        <img src="/images/background.jpg" class="background-image" alt="background"/>
    </section>
    </main>
    <div id="popup-signup" class="modal-wrapper">
    <form class="modal-window">
        <button class="button-close">Close</button>
        <p class="modal-title">Sign Up</p>
        <label>Email:<input type="email" class="input-button" id='signup-email' required/></label><br/>
        <label>Password:<input class="input-button" id='signup-password' type='password' required/></label><br/>
        <label>Name:<input class="input-button" id='userName' required/></label><br/>
        <label>Age:<input type="number" class="input-button" id='userAge' required/></label><br/>
        <label>Weigh:<input type="number" class="input-button" id='userWeight' required/></label><br/>
        <label>Illness:<input class="input-button" id='userIllness' required/></label><br/>
        <button type="submit" class="entries-modal-button" id='signup'>Sign up</button>
    </form>
    </div>
    <div id="popup-login" class="modal-wrapper">
    <form class="modal-window">
        <button class="button-close">Close</button>
        <p class="modal-title">Log In</p>
        <label>Email:<input class="input-button" id='login-email' required/></label><br/>
        <label>Password:<input class="input-button" id='login-password' type='password' required/></label>
        <button type="submit" class="entries-modal-button" id='login'>Log in</button>
    </form>
    </div>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/popup.js"></script>
</body>
</html>